01:52:43,541 --> 01:52:45,375
<i>bencana melanda Kota Pingjing.</i>

1195
01:52:45,458 --> 01:52:46,791
<i>Ada ribut taufan</i>

1196
01:52:46,875 --> 01:52:48,000
<i>dan puting beliung.</i>

1197
01:52:49,083 --> 01:52:51,041
<i>Itu menurut catatan sejarawan.</i>

1198
01:52:51,916 --> 01:52:53,625
<i>Ia cukup berbeza</i>

1199
01:52:53,708 --> 01:52:55,041
<i>daripada catatan saya.</i>

1200
01:52:55,750 --> 01:52:58,875
<i>Pertempuran Jambatan Roh</i>
<i>telah menentukan nasib dunia.</i>

1201
01:52:59,458 --> 01:53:02,291
<i>Qingming dan para khadam</i>
<i>berjuang bermati-matian,</i>

1202
01:53:02,833 --> 01:53:05,000
<i>tapi saya saja yang dipuja</i>

1203
01:53:05,083 --> 01:53:06,583
<i>sebagai wira.</i>

1204
01:53:08,000 --> 01:53:08,833
<i>Qingming.</i>

1205
01:53:10,041 --> 01:53:11,750
<i>Apa yang terjadi kepada awak?</i>

1206
01:53:12,625 --> 01:53:13,750
<i>Saya pun tak pasti.</i>

1207
01:53:15,625 --> 01:53:17,333
<i>Tapi awak nampak begitu tekad</i>

1208
01:53:17,416 --> 01:53:19,125
<i>melepaskan semua khadam awak.</i>

1209
01:53:20,041 --> 01:53:21,875
<i>Saya pasti awak dipaksa melakukannya.</i>

1210
01:53:28,083 --> 01:53:31,166
<i>Pengorbanan awak</i>
<i>membawa keamanan kepada rakyat.</i>

1211
01:53:32,166 --> 01:53:34,125
<i>Tapi khadam awak hidup terkontang-kanting.</i>

1212
01:53:35,291 --> 01:53:38,583
<i>Saya juga sudah tiada tempat kediaman.</i>

1213
01:54:10,625 --> 01:54:11,833
<i>Qingming.</i>

1214
01:54:12,416 --> 01:54:13,875
<i>Tidak kira siapa tuan</i>

1215
01:54:13,958 --> 01:54:15,000
<i>dan siapa khadam,</i>

1216
01:54:16,166 --> 01:54:18,333
<i>kami semua menanti kepulangan awak.</i>

1217
01:54:18,833 --> 01:54:20,833
<i>Kami rela berkongsi derita awak.</i>

1218
01:54:24,291 --> 01:54:26,125
<i>Bukankah tujuan utama mantera khadam</i>

1219
01:54:26,208 --> 01:54:28,250
<i>adalah untuk bersama</i>
<i>dalam susah dan senang,</i>

1220
01:54:28,750 --> 01:54:31,541
<i>hidup dan mati dan takkan mengkhianat?</i>

1221
01:59:56,250 --> 01:59:59,250
Tilikan nasib Tahun Baru Qingming
baru mahu bermula.

1222
02:00:03,416 --> 02:00:06,375
<i>Nampaknya kisah ini belum berakhir lagi.</i>

1223
02:00:06,458 --> 02:00:09,125
Terjemahan sari kata oleh Nursyazela

